{"tid":2025492,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本取消夏季甲子園，二戰後首次","createTime":"2020-05-20T09:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T10:56:17.000Z","uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdd46885271cdf1ad73860413eea90c82e66e1c","tid":2025492,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"【#LikeJapan生活】日本夏季甲子園取消 二戰以來首次 <br />\n 日本高中野球聯盟5月20日宣布，因武漢肺炎疫情，繼3月春季甲子園後，再取消原定8月開打的夏季甲子園，是繼1941年後，79年來首次停辨。<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前日本一度有人發動萬人聯署，希望夏季甲子園能如期舉行，讓一眾高三學生能趕上高中年代的最後一次大賽，以及把握一個進軍職棒的機會。可惜最後始終事與願違，令不少同學夢想破滅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2020/05/20/phpm3i5zh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F20%2Fphpm3i5zh.png&h=69d6f609&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c989304a8b5a3a8e2b07b44b1f130f1aa8099f7e","tid":2025492,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"棒球》震撼！日本戰後第一次 夏季甲子園確定停辦<br />\n<br />\n〔記者龔乃玠／綜合報導〕日本高中野球聯盟今天宣布，受武漢肺炎疫情（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）衝擊，原訂8月開幕的夏季甲子園確定取消，成為1941年以來、日本戰後首度停辦夏甲。<br />\n<br />\n日本在3月才取消高中棒球選拔賽（春季甲子園），未料武漢肺炎疫情延燒至今，先前傳出8月10日開打的夏甲可能取消時，還有萬人連署希望如期開打，只是日本高中野球聯盟今天線上開會仍決定取消，總計49所高校代表隊的甲子園夢碎。<br />\n<br />\n日本夏季甲子園仍在1918年米暴動、1941年戰爭而中止，今年受到疫情衝擊，相隔79年又第三度中止，也是日本戰後以來第一次。關西大學名譽教授宮本勝浩日前評估，夏甲中止將造成672億日圓（約186億台幣）的經濟損失。"},{"pid":"f0c1949a285e41b6d325edc87dba9f761e1d0760","tid":2025492,"uid":2676,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"多謝中國"},{"pid":"b64111d9db05e949bad7ef45c8c7939171a85781","tid":2025492,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c1949a285e41b6d325edc87dba9f761e1d0760","tid":2025492,"uid":2676,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"多謝中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"夏天結束了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ea995c6a2504bc20f33b3f7268ffd719ba511d","tid":2025492,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"培養反中意識"},{"pid":"86c95dba130839941bea3bea45cf97188b81e1fb","tid":2025492,"uid":143260,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"どうもありがとう 支国肺炎"},{"pid":"2c3b831217ee5780dfd4f781944c294166f59707","tid":2025492,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"睇怕日職日乙都無得踢<br />\n今季無日本波賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa578febb3625e67c85e4aa3ef0f0261bbed503d","tid":2025492,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ea995c6a2504bc20f33b3f7268ffd719ba511d","tid":2025492,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"培養反中意識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"上杉達也永遠冇得完夢梗係嬲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b70c1cbcebb320eb4ca877a35f34bdbef64957e","tid":2025492,"uid":72630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"好慘，班高中三年生，諗住打完先屌女神，家陣無左呢個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e374bdab8eadde71739b6c2d59a1706411e473","tid":2025492,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b70c1cbcebb320eb4ca877a35f34bdbef64957e","tid":2025492,"uid":72630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"好慘，班高中三年生，諗住打完先屌女神，家陣無左呢個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"一年級做散仔執波，二年級都係要等三年級畢業先或者練緊團隊，基本上成個高中生涯都係等三年級最後一年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2ad9c96ea59a48cb955b0c21fc2d72b0a902e0","tid":2025492,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"last year個班慘慘"},{"pid":"81289373dcdf12ce4c4b4702cdb9a6df7ff632f8","tid":2025492,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"安達充no 安打"},{"pid":"0480b6d917932ab4dbece43e26bc84ca038d126d","tid":2025492,"uid":165113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"記住係支那人搞到你哋冇咗青春食女嘅美好回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5009ca7117a3e90a93e37a367b67287ac288195f","tid":2025492,"uid":40398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97e4425bde9d23aa5f68aa6e3284e298e66d5ef","tid":2025492,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"點都要要補辦番啦<br />\n咩形式都好"},{"pid":"4ac73d5be2b69eff2847e09ee4553c05147ea635","tid":2025492,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"哎 高3個班喊撚死"},{"pid":"cadb7a0c7ede3423bb94d32afca3e32e460d307f","tid":2025492,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97e4425bde9d23aa5f68aa6e3284e298e66d5ef","tid":2025492,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"點都要要補辦番啦<br />\n咩形式都好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"你畢業大家都散曬啦 點打波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f66a3cddfa06870a842afdf5edf11cec9510dd9","tid":2025492,"uid":188660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n給果係幸運四葉草 青葉就睇唔到光仔時速160公里直球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c